item.title: Making my 508.... help?
item.dc:creator: @Realm_of_Dark Realm of Dark
item.description:
@Realm_of_Dark wrote:

That means the IP the client is trying to connect to is not running. Make sure that the IP is up and running, and if not, make sure it is set to “127.0.0.1” (which is localhost, always running).
